<br>
We had heard that CT popped.  We also heard that someone was killing repops but they were not going for CT or going to stay much longer.  It would have repoped in time for our raid so no big woop to us.<br>
<br>
After midnight sometime I got a /tell saying BoTS is massing around Fear portal.  Well this concerned me at first but I simply contacted them and quickly got a tell from Garmm that they were checking Fear because they heard someone was going for CT.  If they were going FFA BoTS was gonna be right there too is what I took of it.  Well I guess they learned that only 6 players were there.  And after talking briefly they aborted the raid with no fuss.  It was handled with maturity and respect so I have no hard feelings.  There was no arguing simply ok, we are pulling out.  And they were gone in 10 minutes.  Got some good luck wishes on getting my epic item and that was all.<br>
<br>
There was no KS atempt because if they wanted to do it they had noone in the plane to fight over as we were just finishing up killing the overking in Chardok.  I wasn't even going to bring this up but I guess gossip spreads fast on our lil server.<br>
